    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a stapler. Choose a photocopier that always breaks. Choose a screen full of spreadsheets, numbers that mean nothing, and documents no one will ever read. Choose quiet humility. Or..., choose something else?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your job is a mystery.</strong> The files you’re sorting don’t make sense, the letters you type are nonsense. Your coworkers are frighteningly strange, and the office corridors are even more confusing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/4ba04bff0b0ad18edf87e66808078eb9.poster.avif?t=1770712688\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/4ba04bff0b0ad18edf87e66808078eb9.webm?t=1770712688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/4ba04bff0b0ad18edf87e66808078eb9.mp4?t=1770712688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is to become an employee of the month and get a promotion. But the decision is yours to make. Sabotage work and earn harsh punishment? Work hard and get a reward or try to escape?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/c2eabef03ff02f73ca37ada7c1b72e34.poster.avif?t=1770712688\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/c2eabef03ff02f73ca37ada7c1b72e34.webm?t=1770712688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303400/extras/c2eabef03ff02f73ca37ada7c1b72e34.mp4?t=1770712688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit a shrink glued to the sofa, ride the elevator, dance in the party room, and carry out your office routine while solving the mystery. </p>",
